{"id":2755,"date":"2021-05-31T23:01:18","date_gmt":"2021-05-31T16:01:18","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/thocaca.com\/?p=2755"},"modified":"2021-08-22T08:12:58","modified_gmt":"2021-08-22T01:12:58","slug":"cac-buoc-lam-bai-thi-toan-thptqg","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2021\/05\/31\/cac-buoc-lam-bai-thi-toan-thptqg\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00c1C B\u01af\u1edaC L\u00c0M B\u00c0I THI TO\u00c1N THPTQG"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>M\u00ecnh m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i chia s\u1ebb kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m b\u00e0i thi TN THPT m\u00f4n To\u00e1n. Th\u1ef1c ra th\u00ec m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed7i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p, m\u1ed7i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c nhau. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1i form chung c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n th\u00ec b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau \u0111\u00e2y n\u00eau kh\u00e1 l\u00e0 r\u00f5 nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: L\u00e0m b\u00e0i l\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ed9t, c\u00e2u n\u00e0o ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e1p \u00e1n th\u00ec khoanh lu\u00f4n, c\u00e2u n\u00e0o kh\u00f3 qu\u00e1 b\u1ecf qua, \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u ch\u01b0a l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <br>Ch\u00fa \u00fd: Gi\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi b\u1ea5m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eb1ng m\u00e1y Casio tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea5y 2 m\u00e1y t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi.<img loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"&#x1f44c;\" src=\"https:\/\/static.xx.fbcdn.net\/images\/emoji.php\/v9\/t7b\/1\/16\/1f44c.png\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: Quay l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3t 2. N\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng d\u00f9 kh\u00f3 hay d\u1ec5 th\u00ec m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u00e0 0.2 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00ean h\u00e3y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u00fang to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e2u d\u1ec5 nh\u00e9! V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i k\u1ebb v\u1ebd h\u00ecnh chi ti\u1ebft, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebb b\u1eb1ng tay \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Khoanh b\u1eeba t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u ch\u01b0a l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean khoanh theo c\u1ea3m t\u00ednh, m\u00e0 n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 khoanh b\u1eeba (v\u00ed d\u1ee5 to\u00e0n A, to\u00e0n B,&#8230;) t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 tr\u00fang s\u1ebd cao h\u01a1n.<img loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" alt=\"&#x1f44d;\" src=\"https:\/\/static.xx.fbcdn.net\/images\/emoji.php\/v9\/tfc\/1\/16\/1f44d.png\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Ki\u1ec3m tra l\u1ea1i b\u00e0i. B\u01b0\u1edbc ki\u1ec3m tra b\u00e0i c\u1ef1c k\u00ec quan tr\u1ecdng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m tra l\u1ea1i b\u00e0i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb x\u00f3t c\u00e2u ch\u01b0a l\u00e0m ho\u1eb7c ch\u01b0a khoanh. Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ch\u1ec9 \u00f4n t\u1eadp theo \u0111\u1ec1 minh h\u1ecda. C\u1ea7n \u00f4n r\u1ed9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c ra. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00f4n To\u00e1n th\u00ec &#8221; Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p sai c\u00e2u d\u1ec5 v\u00e0 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u00e2u kh\u00f3&#8221; nh\u00e9!&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1ecdc qua c\u00f3 khi t\u1ed1n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian. Nh\u01b0ng m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn share l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m b\u00e0i m\u00f4n To\u00e1n. Ch\u00fac c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u00ec thi TN th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nha!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n: S\u01b0u t\u1ea7m!<\/p>\n<!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on the_content --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on the_content -->","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mh-excerpt\"><p>M\u00ecnh m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i chia s\u1ebb kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m b\u00e0i thi TN THPT m\u00f4n To\u00e1n. Th\u1ef1c ra th\u00ec m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed7i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p, <a class=\"mh-excerpt-more\" href=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2021\/05\/31\/cac-buoc-lam-bai-thi-toan-thptqg\/\" title=\"C\u00c1C B\u01af\u1edaC L\u00c0M B\u00c0I THI TO\u00c1N THPTQG\">[&#8230;]<\/a><!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2756,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[2],"tags":[28],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2755"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2755"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2755\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2758,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2755\/revisions\/2758"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2756"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2755"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2755"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/t